{"tid":1174039,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"官方IG日文「告別平成」南韓網友暴怒瘋狂砲轟！沉默26天…「TWICE」日籍成員Sana爆哭：想守護粉絲","createTime":"2019-05-27T13:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T14:26:02.000Z","uid":9573,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d484abcc1ed2d5e4c0e2529833b5623436d747","tid":1174039,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"南韓女團「TWICE」日籍成員Sana因在官方IG以日文向日本平成年代告別，勾起南韓網友怒火，在網上遭猛烈砲轟「怎麼會在官方IG發舔日文」、「不知道日韓兩國的歷史仇恨嗎」，痛批經紀公司JYP沒教好歷史，甚至要Sana滾回日本。事隔26天，Sana近日首度對此事公開做出回應，哽咽表示很擔心粉絲們消失。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/27/1944208-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F27%2F1944208-XXL.jpg&h=b2abecc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Sana因發文跟平成告別惹怒南韓網友。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/27/1944209-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F27%2F1944209-XXL.jpg&h=290ea0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「TWICE」26日在首爾舉辦演唱會，Sana在台上首度針對「平成事件」吐露內心想法：「現在有很多人知道、喜歡TWICE，團裡的每個人的個性、想法都不一樣，我不知道我說的每一句話會以什麼樣的形式被大家接受，在說話時，就算我沒有那樣的意圖，還是有可能造成很多人失望。」Sana表示在事件發生後思考了很多，很害怕支持她的粉絲會因此消失不見，說著忍不住淚灑舞台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/27/1944206-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F27%2F1944206-XXL.jpg&h=5b9a3fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼Sana在演唱會上哽咽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/27/1944205-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F27%2F1944205-XXL.jpg&h=2c04ed2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AABYzdy.img?h=400&amp;w=356&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=327&amp;y=128\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAABYzdy.img%3Fh%3D400%26w%3D356%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D327%26y%3D128&h=43d4c2ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/05/27/1944216-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F05%2F27%2F1944216-XXL.jpg&h=860ce65f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Sana在IG發文意外掀起韓網上的罵戰。<br />\n<br />\nSana日前在日本天皇退位後，年號更改之際，在TWICE官方IG以日文寫下：「作為平成年代出生的人面對平成 的結束總感覺有些寂寞，但平成辛苦了！讓我們朝著令和這個新的開始出發，愉快的度過平成的最後一天吧。」並標註謝謝平成、令和請多關照，沒想到單純的心情抒發，意外挑起日韓兩國的歷史情結，在韓網上掀起罵戰。"},{"pid":"94a6760279aa7d3ec2f64f58679d4621d64062a8","tid":1174039,"uid":205928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"坐左幾耐"},{"pid":"ef3e300da6f49680e21755be70ca44cc84becf5c","tid":1174039,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AABYzdy.img?h=400&amp;w=356&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=327&amp;y=128\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAABYzdy.img%3Fh%3D400%26w%3D356%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D327%26y%3D128&h=0cd92d62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e911e7601e6c195e423efa49b77d1f4cbbe1eb1a","tid":1174039,"uid":238483,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/67/590x/secondary/Salah-Liverpool-gossip-1569487.jpg?r=1540454163627\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.express.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fdynamic%2F67%2F590x%2Fsecondary%2FSalah-Liverpool-gossip-1569487.jpg%3Fr%3D1540454163627&h=8ede1132&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}